Hugo is your friendly AI companion on the web. It helps you generate content like tweets or blog posts, translate text or gives you information or contenxt. Hugo is easy to use with a simple command in any text box will give generate the content you want. 

✅How to use:

Go to any text box on a website like twitter, reddit and others( see the list below) and enter the Hugo command.

Write the following command:

hugo: write a tweet;[space key]

Once the content is generated please press the space key again so it the text is not deleted, the command will disapear. If you are unhappy with the result you can try the command again.

✅Current supported websites:

Please see our help link here https://brainik.com/hugo-ai-help/. We add new websites and use cases weekly.

✅Limitations:

We limit the text generation to be at 1024 tokens per command, we think this is optimum for generating content quickly.

✅List of commands:

hugo: some text;
rewrite: some text;
spanish: some text;
french: some text;
answer: some text;
grammar: some text;
code: some text;
more soon...

